  <title>Info Dialog</title>
      <p>
          Use the <cmd>--info</cmd> option to create an information dialog.
      </p>

      <p>
        The following example script shows how to create an information dialog:
      </p>

<code>
#!/bin/bash

zenity --info \
--text="Merge complete. Updated 3 of 10 files."
</code>


